parameters.name: Total_Counts
parameters.description: Total number of counts in the accumlation period.

parameters.name: Star_Flag
parameters.description:
Indicates pixel contamination by star light:
                            0 = O.K.
                            1 = pixel contaminated by star light
                           -1 = not yet determined.

parameters.name: Model_Counts
parameters.description:
Counts per second as calculated along the line of sight from a model 
                        (dummy value = -99.)
